	    <listitem>
	      <para>
		Label compression was not always enabled, leading to large reply packets sometimes.
	      </para
	    </listitem>
	    <listitem>
	      <para>
		Database errors on TCP server lead to a nameserver reload by the guardian.
	      </para
	    </listitem>
	    <listitem>
	      <para>
